We can easily get basic statistics about users:

user.stats
{'answers': 414,
 'blogs': None,
 'edits': 7,
 'followers': 640,
 'following': 200,
 'name': 'Christopher J. Su',
 'posts': 8,
 'questions': 107,
 'topics': None,
 'username': 'Christopher-J-Su'}

In addition to that we can also gather:
- followers list
- following list

And some statistics about questions:

We can gather statistics about question like:
- number of answers
- topics (connected with particular question)
- related questions